- **Persistence**: All data (expenses + budget + categories) is saved locally.
- **Time Filters**: Smart filtering by Day/Month/Year.
- **Polish**: Smooth fade-in animations when switching views and full Accessibility (ARIA) support.
- **Support**: Integrated Help option in Settings.
- **PWA Ready**: Installable on mobile devices with offline support!
- **Dark Mode**: Toggle a sleek dark theme in Settings.

## How to Test
1.  **Open [index.html](file:///C:/Users/Subrata%20Das/.gemini/antigravity/brain/861e764a-99a8-4932-a16c-0fb431fca6ff/index.html)**: Open the file in Chrome, Safari, or Edge.
2.  **Install App**: If on mobile (or desktop Chrome), look for "Add to Home Screen" or the Install icon in the address bar.
3.  **Test Smart Shortcuts**:
    - Click **+ (FAB)**.
    - Click the **Microphone** icon. Watch it listen and type for you!
    - Click the **Camera** icon. Watch it scan and extract the amount!
4.  **Test Everything Else**:
    - Add real expenses, create categories, check your stats, and stick to your budget.
    - Notice the smooth fade animation when you click the bottom nav icons!
    - Check the **Settings** view for the new "Help & Support" button.
    - **Try the Dark Mode Toggle!**

